						a diagram of a pendulum with an arm of length L and displacement of theta
						and a bob of mass m and the forces acting on the mass
					</p>
				</description>
				<latex-image><![CDATA[
				\begin{tikzpicture}[scale=0.5]
				\draw[very thick] (0,-0.5) -- ++(90:5) -- ++(300:4.5) ++(300:0.5) coordinate(BOB);
